name: 2025 9th International Conference on Materials Engineering and Nano Sciences
content: Publication: The accepted and registered papers will be published in below listed journals of【Scientific.Net】collection, which will be indexed by【Scopus】, Inspec, Chemical Abstracts Service, Google Scholar etc. \*Defect and Diffusion Forum (DDF) (ISSN print 1012-0386/ISSN web 1662-9507) \*Solid State Phenomena (SSP) (ISSN print 1012-0394/ISSN web 1662-9779) \*Materials Science Forum (MSF) ISSN print 0255-5476/ISSN web 1662-9752) \*Key Engineering Materials (KEM) (ISSN print 1013-9826/ISSN web 1662-9795) You can visit at https://www.scientific.net/ for more information.
organizers: Kwansei Gakuin University, Japan and Chiba University, Japan
